      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like there are these hidden costs taking a bite out of my money before it even hits the actual debt. like, why does it feel so much more aggressive in the beginning? is there some kind of mathematical drag that makes it harder to make progress early on?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
